CustomField.formula:
/*If an Academic Interest exists for the Opportunity, retrieve the associated Department from the Academic Interest*/ 
IF(NOT(ISBLANK(Academic_Interest__c)),(  Academic_Interest__r.Department__r.Name  ), 

/*If not, retrieve the associated Department from the Recruitment Interset on the Opportunity*/ 
(  Recruitment_Interest__r.Department__r.Name  ))
